  <brief_title>Use of Low Sensitivity Pregnancy Test for Self-assessment of Medical Abortion</brief_title>
  <acronym>m-Assist+</acronym>
  <official_title>The Feasibility of Replacing In-person Follow-up for Early Medical Abortion With a Low Sensitivity Pregnancy Test, Symptom Checklist and Text Messages in the South African Public Sector Setting.</official_title>
